Print Methods

# S3 method for SOA
print(x, ...)

# S3 method for MDLE
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

object to be printed (SOA, OSOA, MDLE)
...

further arguments for function print

Examples

myOSOA <- OSOAs_regular(s=3, k=3, optimize=FALSE)
print(myOSOA)
